<template>
    
    <JenesiusModal  >
      
      <button @click="ClosePopUp">close</button>
    </JenesiusModal>
</template>

<script>
import { JenesiusModal } from "jenesius-vue-modal";


export default {
    name: "UpdatePopUp", 
    components:{
        JenesiusModal
    }, 
    methods:{
        ClosePopUp(){
            this.$router.push('/displayList');
            alert("Task Updated Successfully");
        }
    }
}
</script>
